of the undertext in the Syriac Galen Palimpsest.</gtr:impact><gtr:outcomeId>58c6c1039b9843.73943489</gtr:outcomeId><gtr:title>Canonical Variate Analysis Software for Dimensionality Reduction with Application to Image Processing</gtr:title><gtr:type>Software</gtr:type><gtr:url>https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.154129</gtr:url><gtr:yearFirstProvided>2016</gtr:yearFirstProvided></gtr:softwareAndTechnicalProductOutput></gtr:softwareAndTechnicalProductOutputs><gtr:spinOutOutputs/></gtr:output><gtr:publications><gtr:publication><gtr:id>7D8BF44B-C12A-4E69-BA7F-0EED909D8998</gtr:id><gtr:title>Interdisciplinarity: Inside Manchester's 'arts lab'.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Nature</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/0f4c5b12a8b2471140344173729eb977"><gtr:id>0f4c5b12a8b2471140344173729eb977</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Pormann PE</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2015-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0028-0836</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>58c6c381e9ea81.54710212</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>08CBAFAB-9263-4553-91CD-E834B7041595</gtr:id><gtr:title>Continuing research on the Syriac Galen Palimpsest: collaborative implementation within the framework of two European projects</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Semitica et Classica</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/34ef84ad9970f1cc8229dd110757e8b5"><gtr:id>34ef84ad9970f1cc8229dd110757e8b5</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Afif N</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2016-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>58c6b39b35ac73.08275313</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>D255955E-9611-4D26-A9EC-100B610C5AA9</gtr:id><gtr:title>The Syriac Galen Palimpsest: Research Methods and Latest Discoveries</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Comparative Oriental Manuscript Studies Bulletin</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/bc25